description: Excellent service . Vvv responsible and caring also very professional. I would recommend to anyone looking to move their old parents to their home country via stretcher and on a commercial flight. A v big thank you to each and every staff member who made it possible for my mother who was critically ill in a hospital in Dubai from the hospital to the airport and then from mumbai airport to a hospital in mumbai effortlessly

Best service ever. Very professional and accurate. Dealing with Humanitarian services and especially Mansour was a great experience. They were really our savers and our backbone to help going through very difficult moments during the repatriation of the body of our late colleague to his home town. Really much appreciated

Excellent service provider!!Fast, well organized and very professional! And of course excellent communication with their customers! I recommend Air Ambulance Dubai Human care worldwide for all travelers to Europe.
